query:
INSERT INTO collections (
                id, name, game, game_version, created, modified, last_played
            )
            VALUES (
                $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7
            )
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                name = $2,
                game = $3,
                game_version = $4,
                created = $5,
                modified = $6,
                last_played = $7
